<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">خاموش یا محدود کردن ردیابی تاریخچهٔ پرونده</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents pagewide">
<p class="p">Tracking recently used files and folders makes it easier to find
  items that you have been working on in the file manager and in file
  dialogs in applications. You may wish to keep your file usage history
  private instead, or only track your very recent history.</p>
<div class="steps"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-steps"><h2><span class="title">ردیابی تاریخچه پرونده را خاموش کنید</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><ol class="steps">
<li class="steps"><p class="p">نمای کلی <span class="gui"><a href="shell-introduction.html.fa#activities" title="نمای کلی فعّالیت‌ها">فعّالیت‌ها</a></span> را گشوده و شروع به نوشتن <span class="gui">محرمانگی و امنیت</span> کنید.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Select <span class="guiseq"><span class="gui">Settings</span> ◂ <span class="gui">Privacy &amp; Security</span></span> from the
      results. This will open the <span class="gui">Privacy &amp; Security</span> panel.</p></li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">برای گشودن تابلو <span class="gui">تاریخچهٔ پرونده و زباله‌دان</span> را بزنید.</p></li>
<li class="steps">
<p class="p">Switch the <span class="gui">File History</span> switch to off.</p>
<p class="p">To re-enable this feature, switch the <span class="gui">File History</span> switch
     to on.</p>
</li>
<li class="steps"><p class="p">Use the <span class="gui">Clear History…</span> button to purge the history
      immediately.</p></li>
</ol></div>
</div></div>
<div class="note" title="نکته">
